So first of all--

00:57:34.224 --> 00:57:35.640
AUDIENCE: So the
universe shrinks?

00:57:35.640 --> 00:57:38.510
MAX TEGMARK: We have
to be careful with how

00:57:38.510 --> 00:57:40.420
we use our words here.

00:57:40.420 --> 00:57:42.452
Some people choose to
